Document: CubemapArray
Path: godot/classes/class_cubemaparray.rst
Summary: Method to create a placeholder version of the CubemapArray resource

Resource create_placeholder() const

Creates a placeholder version of this resource (PlaceholderCubemapArray). This method generates a lightweight version of the CubemapArray that can be used for previewing or when the actual resource is not yet available. The placeholder does not contain actual cubemap data but maintains the structure and metadata of the original resource.